**Performance & Security**

- Access to Java 25 LTS with extended support until September 2033
- Latest security patches bundled with Java 25 runtime
- Performance improvements including enhanced virtual threads and GC optimizations

**Developer Productivity**

- Modern language features: pattern matching, records (fully available in Java 25)
- Improved IDE support and Spring Boot 3.2 integration
- Virtual threads and structured concurrency for scalable async operations

**Future-Ready Foundation**

- Compatible with modern frameworks and cloud-native deployments
- Positioned for Spring Boot 4.x adoption
- Ready for adoption of latest Java features in new development

